奶抱，晚上睡觉说梦话就叫奶奶，平时嘴里叫的最多的还是奶奶… 说实话我现在看到他就有一种，我真的不想管他了，既然我这么真心对你，受了那么多苦把你生下来，尽心尽力的带你，你还是只要奶奶，那我还不如出去工作去，你就跟着奶奶算了。 可我又想做个称职的妈妈，我自己本身是单亲家庭，我并不希望我的孩子有些什么问题，我在想，是不是我的心理有些什么问题了，希望能在知乎上看到答案，是我有问题吗？或者有什么解决方法吗？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-ba1b55825bbe214c36e755d8d7540f81_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/606034442"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I7ubtwfe/h+JoEAMaCDk2OTU0Mzk5IKnolqQGMAA4twFAIXIIOTY5NTQzOTl4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1686766187.641181", "card_id": "Q_604621748", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 324}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "时间真的可以治愈一切吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "37 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604621748"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I7ubtwfe/h+JoEAMaCDk2NjQwNTM1IOjy7KMGMAA44wJAInIIOTY2NDA1MzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "35_1686766187.641469", "card_id": "Q_604775983", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 241}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在领悟了什么道理后，你的人生从此轻松起来？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-6c8f4e5e8b85c4bfc6805999e831ce39_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "37 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/604775983"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I7ubtwfe/h+JoEAMaCDk2Njc0ODI1IL3B8qMGMAA4hwRAI3IIOTY2NzQ4MjV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "36_1